  "abstract": "Breeding for resistance to the most devastating foliar diseases of groundnut, the leasfspots and rust has received the highest priority in the groundnut breeding program at ICRISAt.  More than 400 single, triple and double crosses were made using 12 rust and 9 late leafspot resistant germplasm lines.",
